				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "A coarse and unempathetic duergar, one of three guarding some Deep Rothe (beasts of burden currently being used to clear rubble).\r\nDifferent reactions if:\r\n- animals are panicking;\r\n- animals are calm;\r\n- animals are dead (doesn't matter how);"
				}
